This is a remake of the original bh_aztec created 10 years ago by Teh Noob which can be found here.

Basically fixed some things with the original map, doubled the length. Made it a basic bitch ass dev map. Probably going to receive hate for it but atleast pez will have another strafe map to run. I felt like doing this because it is one of my favorite maps and nobody else has done this.
